msgid ""
"Confirming a quotation automatically creates a dedicated project in the "
"Project app. Each new project comes with several default tasks to get you "
"started."
msgstr ""
"確認報價後，系統會自動在專案應用程式中，建立專屬的專案項目。每個新建專案都會"
"預先加入幾項預設任務，助你快速開展工作。"

